\begin_layout Example
举个简单的例子：在质量为
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

的点状费米子上的散射，只考虑树图阶，这时候 
\begin_inset Formula $T_{T}\left(\nu,Q^{2}\right)$
\end_inset

 和 
\begin_inset Formula $F_{T}\left(\nu,Q^{2}\right)$
\end_inset

 都可以被显式计算。此情况下的振幅 
\begin_inset Formula $T_{T}$
\end_inset

等于
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
2T_{T}\left(\nu,Q^{2}\right)=\frac{2m\nu}{2m\nu-Q^{2}}+\frac{2m\nu}{2m\nu+Q^{2}}=\frac{1}{1-x}+\frac{1}{1+x},\label{eq:mu11}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

此处
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & 2m\nu-Q^{2}=2m\frac{P\cdot q}{m}-Q^{2}=\left(P+q\right)^{2}-m^{2}+i\varepsilon\\
